Desiderata:
 conditional expectations
 sequential expectations
 declarative language for expressing expectations

Google Docs: requirements document for expectations language
  a declarative language of expectations
 simple:
  polling:
    "speed SHOULD BE-BELOW 100"
  duration:
    "SHOULD TAKE LESS-THAN 100"
 delay:
  "IN 2 seconds speed SHOULD BE-ABOVE 20"
 conditional:
  "WHEN bark.actor IS $dog THEN bark.object SHOULD BE $animate"
 sequential:
  "action SHOULD NOT-EQUAL action AT -1 STEP"
